<HEAD>Birthday Celebrant Arrested For Drinking 45 Minutes Too Early</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ORANGE, Conn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man was arrested for underage drinking
after liquor control agents found him getting a 45-minute head start
on celebrating his 21st birthday.
   Michael Luetjen, a University of New Haven junior, was drinking
about 11:15 p.m. Nov. 5 at a restaurant when the agents arrived on a
