companies and stores to consider helping the Jan Stuart Skin Care
Co., which for eight years has produced natural ingredient men's
shaving and skin care products.
   ``Maybe they'd be interested,'' Trump told Stuart.
   Stuart said Trump told him that ``a guy willing to risk his
health needs to be heard by the right people.''
